Package com.cafean.JobStatus.tree

Class IndicatorIcon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.JobStatus.tree.IndicatorIcon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.Icon
    public class IndicatorIcon
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.Icon
    An Icon implementation that composites a status indicator over another icon. Icons that do not display an indicator, but wish to accurately conserve the indicator space may supply only a base icon, and the resulting composite will preserve the appropriate amount of space. To provide this guarantee, indicator icons must have a fixed size of 11 pixels wide by 12 pixels tall. IndicatorIcons are not guaranteed to be 16x16 pixels, and probably never will be.
